title: Should we accompany a floor Cool Cats NFT with every new DAOquisition?
body: With more DAOs popping up and purchasing blue chips, we can add a unique element to our strategy / stick to our CC roots by purchasing a floor CC with every new purchase.  This will be our "signature" move, and could be a really strong play from a marketing & branding perspective.
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
